com.etouch.taf.core.datamanager.excel

Class TestDataContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.etouch.taf.core.datamanager.excel.TestDataContainer

  • public class TestDataContainer
extends Object
    Container to store: 1. The test data in format Object[][] with TestDataKey as the key to access the test data. Any TestNG DataProvider implementation that reads data is expected to store the data here for sharing with other test methods requiring the same data. 2. The data files in a map -
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    eTouch Systems Corporation
